  [Ronald Sibanda 26, Luke Jukelile 56; Wonder Nhleko 72]
[Jul 21, Blantyre (moved from May 19 on request South Africa)]
Malawi      1-0 South Africa 
  [Patrick Mabedi 83pen]

Semifinals 
[Aug 18, Lusaka]
Zambia      1-1 Angola            [2-4 pen]
  [Chaswe Nsofwa 36; Fabrice 'Akwa' Maceio 11]
[Aug 25, Blantyre]
Malawi      0-2 Zimbabwe
  [Edzai Kasinauyo 21, Maxwell Dube 58]

Final 

First Leg [Sep 16, Luanda]
Angola      0-0 Zimbabwe
  
Second Leg [Sep 30, Harare]
Zimbabwe    0-1 Angola
  [Flavio Amado 87]


